validated theirs I know   individuals  I define  knowing  as a mutual ability to look at a photograph of the other person and identify him or her by first and last name  Of these   most were immediately disqualified as  neutral  meaning my actions have had neither a positive nor a negative impact on their lives  OR that my actions have had an equally positive and negative impact  of individuals   were identified as  non neutral  actors  Of these  it was determined that I had a net positive impact on at least   and a net negative impact on at least     were classified as  non neutral without category  meaning that I impacted their life  but a positive or negative skew remains ambivalent Furthermore  this study was deeply flawed  there was a confirmation bias as a result of
